title: Your 'Deep' quote
body:
Hey
I just made this so I can see what your 'Good' or 'Deep' quotes are, from YOU!!!

Mine is:
'Girls are so happy, they can bright up the darkest rooms'

replies.body: Omg I forgot about this one lmao
People die if they are killed.
You were a chapter in my life, I was a line in yours. <3
"lemme take u to da movies shawwty"

Nautilus.

And

"LoL is a team game, bro, a team game. Let that sink in."

Oka guys, new one, just unbothered to make another conversation:
Your best pick up line (to all genders)
"It's so deep I can't roll in it."
